        "uuid": "msg-001",
        "text": "How should I design an interface for a storage backend?",
        "sender": "human",
        "created_at": "2024-06-15T09:00:00.000000+00:00"
      },
      {
        "uuid": "msg-002",
        "text": "I'd recommend starting with the minimal set of operations your callers actually need.",
        "sender": "assistant",
        "created_at": "2024-06-15T09:01:00.000000+00:00"
      },
      {
        "uuid": "msg-003",
        "text": "That makes sense. What about error handling?",
        "sender": "human",
        "created_at": "2024-06-15T09:03:00.000000+00:00"
      },
      {
        "uuid": "msg-004",
        "text": "Return errors from the interface methods and let callers decide how to handle them.",
        "sender": "assistant",
        "created_at": "2024-06-15T09:05:00.000000+00:00"
      }
    ]
